<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ن غ ي:</span> <span class="c2">(الْمُنَاغَاةُ)</span> الْمُغَازَلَةُ. وَالْمَرْأَةُ <span class="c2">(تُنَاغِي)</span> الصَّبِيَّ أَيْ تُكَلِّمُهُ بِمَا يُعْجِبُهُ وَيَسُرُّهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>